## 1. Application Overview

**Netra Analytics** is a multi-tenant, privacy-first, no-code behavioral analytics platform that collects, processes, and visualizes user behavior data across web, mobile, and game engine platforms. The name "Netra" means *eye* in Sanskrit — symbolizing deep visibility into user behavior.

### Core Pillars
| Pillar | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| **Zero-Code Tracking** | DOM Autocapture + Visual Event Tagger — no developer coding required |
| **Cross-Platform** | 9 platform SDKs/plugins from WordPress to Unity to iOS |
| **Real-Time** | Sub-second data pipeline via Kafka → ClickHouse |
| **Privacy-First** | GDPR/CCPA compliant, cookieless, PII sanitization by default |
| **Open-Source Stack** | 100% open-source technologies, no vendor lock-in |
| **Multi-Tenant** | Isolated workspaces, team collaboration, role-based access |

---

## 2. SaaS Storefront (Public-Facing Website)

The public storefront markets the product, drives trial sign-ups, and serves as the documentation hub.

### 2.1 Marketing & Landing Pages
- **Hero Section** — Animated value proposition with live demo embed
- **Feature Showcase** — Interactive cards for Autocapture, Visual Tagger, Real-Time dashboards
- **Platform Integrations Page** — Visual grid of all 9 supported platforms with logos
- **Pricing Page** — Tiered pricing with interactive plan calculator (Free / Starter / Pro / Enterprise)
- **Competitor Comparison Page** — Side-by-side vs. Google Analytics, Mixpanel, Amplitude
- **About / Story Page** — Mission, team bios, open-source philosophy
- **Blog / Changelog** — Technical articles, product updates, SEO-optimized content
- **Roadmap Page** — Public product roadmap (Kanban-style, e.g. via Canny or built-in)

### 2.2 Authentication & Onboarding
- **Sign Up** — Email + password, Google OAuth, GitHub OAuth
- **Email Verification** — Magic link email verification
- **Login** — Session-based with JWT refresh tokens
- **Forgot Password / Reset** — Secure email-based reset flow
- **Workspaces Onboarding Wizard** — 4-step guided setup after registration:
  1. Create Workspace / Project
  2. Choose platform (select from 9 options)
  3. Install tracking snippet/plugin (copy-paste or download)
  4. Verify data is flowing (live ping indicator)

### 2.3 Documentation & Developer Hub
- **Quick Start Guides** — Per-platform installation guides with code samples
- **API Reference** — Interactive OpenAPI/Swagger UI
- **SDK Reference Docs** — Per-SDK methods, events, and properties reference
- **Video Tutorials** — Embedded walkthroughs
- **Search** — Full-text documentation search (Algolia DocSearch)
- **Changelog** — Versioned release notes

### 2.4 Trust & Compliance
- **Privacy Policy** page (GDPR/CCPA compliant)
- **Terms of Service** page
- **Cookie-Free Badge** — Cookieless tracking certification display
- **Security Page** — Data encryption, SOC2 commitments, penetration test disclosure
- **Status Page** — Real-time system uptime dashboard (e.g., Statuspage.io)

### 2.5 Conversion Funnels
- **Live Demo** — Sandbox workspace pre-loaded with sample data
- **Free Trial CTA** — No credit card required
- **Testimonials / Case Studies** — Social proof from e-commerce, mobile app, and gaming customers
- **Contact / Sales Form** — Enterprise inquiry with CRM integration

