## 4. User Dashboard & Analytics Dashboard

This is the primary product delivered to paying customers — their personal analytics workspace.

### 4.1 Workspace & Project Settings
- **Project Management** — Create multiple projects per workspace (e.g., website + mobile app)
- **Tracking Snippet** — One-click copy of JS snippet, API key management
- **Team Invitations** — Invite team members via email with role assignment
- **Domain Allowlist** — Whitelist authorized domains for data ingestion
- **Data Retention Settings** — Self-service data retention duration selector
- **Notification Preferences** — Email/Slack alerts for anomaly detection

### 4.2 Visual Event Tagger (No-Code)
- **Website Iframe Loader** — Load own website inside the SaaS dashboard
- **Element Hover Highlighter** — Visual DOM overlay showing hovered element boundaries
- **Click-to-Define Events** — Click any element to open event naming dialog
- **Event Rule Library** — List of all defined tracking rules (CSS selectors → event names)
- **Rule Testing** — Live test that a rule fires correctly before saving
- **Rule Categories** — Organize rules into groups (e.g., "Checkout Events", "Navigation Events")

### 4.3 Real-Time Dashboard
- **Live Event Stream** — Live-scrolling feed of events as they are captured
- **Active Users Now** — Realtime count of users currently on site/app
- **Real-Time Map** — World map with live geographic user locations
- **Top Pages Right Now** — Pages with most active users at this moment
- **Realtime UTM Sources** — Where current visitors came from

### 4.4 Audience & User Analytics
- **Unique Visitors** — Daily/weekly/monthly unique visitor counts
- **New vs. Returning Users** — Trend chart with breakdown
- **User Profiles** — Per-user event timelines (anonymized or identified)
- **User Segments / Cohorts** — Define and save user groups by behavior or properties
- **Geo-Location Breakdown** — Country, region, city level traffic breakdown
- **Device & Browser Breakdown** — OS, browser, screen resolution stats
- **Language Distribution** — User language preferences

### 4.5 Traffic Analytics
- **Pageviews & Sessions** — Time-series charts with date range picker
- **Bounce Rate** — Per-page and overall bounce rate trends
- **Session Duration** — Average and distribution of session lengths
- **Entry & Exit Pages** — Top landing pages and exit points
- **Traffic Sources** — Direct, organic search, referral, social, email, paid
- **UTM Campaign Tracking** — Source, medium, campaign, term, content tracking
- **Referrer Breakdown** — Top referring domains

### 4.6 E-Commerce Analytics (WooCommerce / Magento / Shopify / PrestaShop)
- **Revenue Dashboard** — Total revenue, ARPU, GMV trends
- **Conversion Rate** — Visit → add to cart → checkout → purchase funnel
- **Top Products** — Best-selling products by revenue and quantity
- **Cart Abandonment Rate** — % of carts abandoned at each checkout step
- **Average Order Value (AOV)** — Trend over time
- **Coupon Usage Tracking** — Which promo codes drive most revenue
- **Refund Rate** — Refunds over time against total revenue

### 4.7 Funnel Analysis
- **Custom Funnel Builder** — Drag-and-drop multi-step funnel definition
- **Drop-off Visualization** — Funnel chart showing % drop at each step
- **Funnel Segmentation** — Filter funnel by device, UTM source, cohort
- **Conversion Rate Benchmarks** — Compare funnel performance over time periods
- **A/B Funnel Comparison** — Compare two date ranges or user segments

### 4.8 Retention & Cohort Analysis
- **Cohort Retention Matrix** — Heatmap grid (week 0 → week N) by signup cohort
- **Retention Curve** — N-day retention % trend line chart
- **Feature Retention** — Which features keep users coming back
- **Power Users** — Identify "power users" (top 10% by event count)
- **Churned Users** — Identify users who have not returned in X days

### 4.9 Event Explorer
- **Event List** — All captured events with timestamp, user, properties
- **Event Property Inspector** — Drill down into individual event payloads
- **Custom Event Filtering** — Filter by event name, user, date, property value
- **Event Volume Chart** — Events over time per event name
- **Property Breakdown** — Breakdown any event by a property dimension

### 4.10 Reports & Exports
- **Custom Report Builder** — Compose multi-widget reports from any metric
- **Scheduled Email Reports** — Send weekly/monthly PDF reports to team
- **Dashboard Templates** — Pre-built report templates (E-commerce, Mobile App, SaaS)
- **CSV / JSON Export** — Export any dataset for external analysis
- **API Access** — REST API to pull analytics data into external BI tools

### 4.11 Mobile App Analytics (Android / iOS / React Native)
- **Screen Views** — App screen navigation tracking
- **Session Tracking** — App open, active time, background, close
- **Crash Rate** — % of sessions ending in a crash (with crash context)
- **Device Performance Monitor** — App load time, frame rate stats
- **Push Notification Analytics** — Delivered, opened, converted
- **In-App Purchase Tracking** — IAP events, revenue from purchases
- **App Version Distribution** — Usage by app version

### 4.12 Game Analytics (Unity)
- **Player Session Length** — Average and distribution of play sessions
- **Level Completion Rates** — % of players completing each game level
- **Level Drop-off Funnel** — Where players stop progressing
- **Virtual Economy Tracking** — In-game currency spent/earned events
- **Monetization Dashboard** — IAP revenue, conversion to paying player
- **DAU/MAU Ratio** — Daily/Monthly active user stickiness ratio
- **Player Journey Map** — Sankey diagram of player event flows

### 4.13 Alerts & Anomaly Detection
- **Custom Alert Builder** — Set thresholds on any metric
- **Anomaly Detection** — Auto-detect unusual spikes/drops in events
- **Alert Channels** — Email, Slack webhook, PagerDuty integration
- **Alert History** — Log of all triggered alerts

