## 5. Data Collection Plugins & SDKs

All platforms transmit a standardized JSON event payload to the central ingestion API.

### Standard Event Payload Schema
```json
{
  "tenant_id": "uuid",
  "project_id": "uuid",
  "session_id": "uuid",
  "user_id": "hashed_string",
  "event_name": "string",
  "timestamp": "ISO8601",
  "platform": "web|android|ios|unity|react_native",
  "device": { "type": "mobile|desktop|tablet", "os": "string", "browser": "string" },
  "geo": { "country": "string", "city": "string" },
  "properties": { "key": "value" }
}
```

---

### 5.1 WordPress Plugin
**Plugin Name:** `netra-analytics-for-wordpress`
**Distribution:** WordPress.org Plugin Directory

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **Auto Script Injection** | Uses `wp_head` hook to inject tracking JS on all pages |
| **Admin Settings Page** | Enter API key, configure options |
| **WooCommerce Integration** | Hooks into `woocommerce_thankyou` for server-side purchase events |
| **Order Revenue Tracking** | Sends order total, product array, coupon codes via backend HTTP POST |
| **User Identity** | Passes hashed WordPress user ID for logged-in user tracking |
| **Excluded Roles** | Option to exclude Admins from being tracked |
| **Custom Post Type Events** | Auto-tracks CPT page views |
| **GDPR Consent Hook** | Integrates with GDPR plugins (WP Consent API) before activating tracking |
| **Script Async Loading** | Loads tracking script asynchronously to not block page rendering |

---

### 5.2 WooCommerce Plugin
*(Bundled within the WordPress plugin as an optional WooCommerce module)*

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **View Product Event** | Fires on single product pages |
| **Add to Cart Event** | JS event on add-to-cart action |
| **Checkout Started Event** | Fires when checkout page is loaded |
| **Purchase Event (Server-Side)** | `woocommerce_thankyou` PHP hook → backend API call |
| **Cart Abandonment Tracking** | Tracks sessions ending without completing checkout |
| **Product Search Tracking** | Tracks search queries and result counts |
| **Revenue Attribution** | Associates revenue with UTM source/medium |
| **Refund Event** | `woocommerce_order_refunded` hook fires refund event |

---

### 5.3 Magento 2 Extension
**Extension Name:** `Netra_Analytics`
**Distribution:** Packagist / Github / Magento Marketplace

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **Layout XML Injection** | Uses `default.xml` to inject script block into `<head>` |
| **Order Observer** | Listens to `checkout_submit_all_after` event |
| **Server-Side Purchase** | Dispatches order data via Magento message queue → REST POST |
| **Customer Hash** | Hashes customer email using SHA-256 before sending |
| **Category & Product View** | Tracks catalog browsing events |
| **Admin Configuration** | Magento `System > Configuration` panel for API key |
| **Multi-Store** | Per-store API key configuration for multi-store setups |
| **CSP Whitelist** | Auto-adds Netra CDN to Magento's CSP whitelist |

