| **Order Webhook** | Shopify `orders/paid` webhook → server-side purchase event |
| **Product & Collection Views** | Tracks product and collection page views |
| **Search Tracking** | Tracks Shopify predictive search events |
| **Checkout Funnel** | Tracks cart → checkout → payment → order_paid steps |
| **Customer Identification** | Hashes Shopify customer ID for cross-session linking |
