### 5.6 Unity SDK
**Package:** `NetraAnalytics.unitypackage` / Unity Package Manager (UPM)
**Language:** C#

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **Persistent Game Object** | `DontDestroyOnLoad` singleton manager |
| **Session Tracking** | Auto-tracks session start, pause (`OnApplicationPause`), resume, end |
| **Scene View Events** | Auto-fires `$scene_view` on scene loads |
| **Custom Event API** | `Netra.Track("Level_Complete", properties)` |
| **Level Progress Tracking** | Built-in helpers for level_start, level_complete, level_fail |
| **IAP Revenue Tracking** | Hooks into Unity IAP to track purchase revenue |
| **Ad Impression Tracking** | Integration with Unity Ads impression events |
| **Offline Queue** | SQLite-backed offline event queue; auto-flush on reconnect |
| **Batch Sending** | Sends events in micro-batches (default: 20 events or every 30s) |
| **Performance Safe** | All HTTP calls on background thread; zero main-thread blocking |
| **iOS ATT Handling** | Requests App Tracking Transparency on iOS builds |
| **PC/Mac/WebGL/Android/iOS** | Supports all Unity build targets |

