### 5.7 Android Native SDK
**Language:** Kotlin (Java compatible)
**Distribution:** Maven Central / JitPack

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **Lifecycle Callbacks** | `Application.ActivityLifecycleCallbacks` for auto screen tracking |
| **Session Management** | Auto session start/end based on foreground/background state |
| **Screen View Events** | Auto-captures `$screen_view` on every `Activity` / `Fragment` |
| **Custom Event API** | `Netra.track("button_clicked", properties)` |
| **User Identification** | `Netra.identify("user_id", traits)` for logged-in users |
| **Device Properties** | Auto-captures device model, Android OS version, screen size |
| **Offline Queue** | Room DB (SQLite) buffering with exponential retry |
| **Crash Tracking** | `Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler` captures fatal crashes |
| **Push Token Tracking** | FCM token capture and association with user profile |
| **Foreground Service** | Optional background session extension |
| **Privacy (GDPR)** | `Netra.optOut()` method; no PII stored raw |

---

### 5.8 React Native SDK
**Language:** TypeScript / JavaScript
**Distribution:** npm (`@netra/react-native`)

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **AppState Tracking** | Uses React Native `AppState` API for session management |
| **Navigation Tracking** | Auto-integration with React Navigation and Expo Router |
| **Custom Event API** | `Netra.track("event_name", {props})` async method |
| **User Identification** | `Netra.identify(userId, traits)` |
| **Async Storage Queue** | Uses `@react-native-async-storage/async-storage` for offline events |
| **Platform Detection** | Auto-detects iOS vs Android and sets `platform` property |
| **Expo Compatible** | Works with bare and managed Expo workflows |
| **TypeScript Types** | Full TypeScript type definitions included |
| **Error Boundary Hook** | `NetraErrorBoundary` component to capture JS crashes |
| **IDFA / AAID** | Supports optional advertising ID collection with user consent |

---

### 5.9 iOS Native SDK
**Language:** Swift (Objective-C compatible)
**Distribution:** Swift Package Manager (SPM) / CocoaPods

| Feature | Details |
|---------|---------|
| **Method Swizzling** | Swizzles `viewDidAppear` on `UIViewController` for auto screen tracking |
| **Session Management** | `UIApplication.didBecomeActiveNotification` / `willResignActiveNotification` |
| **Custom Event API** | `Netra.shared.track("event_name", properties: [:])` |
| **User Identification** | `Netra.shared.identify(userId: "id", traits: [:])` |
| **UserDefaults Queue** | Offline event buffer persisted in `UserDefaults` / SQLite |
| **ATT Framework** | Handles Apple App Tracking Transparency prompt and IDFA collection |
| **SwiftUI Support** | `NetraView` wrapper and `.netraTrack()` view modifier |
| **Crash Tracking** | `NSSetUncaughtExceptionHandler` for crash state capture |
| **Push Notification** | APNs token capture and attribution tracking |
| **Background Sessions** | `URLSession` background transfer for queued events |

