## 6. Detailed Tech Stack

### 6.1 Frontend

| Category | Technology | Purpose |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| **Framework** | Next.js 15 (App Router) | SSR/SSG for storefront, CSR for dashboards |
| **Language** | TypeScript | Full type safety across frontend & backend |
| **UI Library** | Shadcn UI + Radix UI | Accessible, unstyled components with full DOM control |
| **CSS** | Tailwind CSS v4 | Utility-first styling; custom design tokens |
| **Charting** | Apache ECharts (via echarts-for-react) | Canvas-based rendering for high-density analytics charts |
| **State Management** | Zustand | Lightweight global state for dashboard filters |
| **Data Fetching** | TanStack Query (React Query) | Server state, caching, background refetching |
| **Forms** | React Hook Form + Zod | Type-safe form handling and schema validation |
| **Animations** | Framer Motion | Micro-animations, page transitions |
| **Icons** | Lucide React | Consistent SVG icon set |
| **Tables** | TanStack Table | Virtualized, sortable, filterable data tables |
| **Date Picker** | react-day-picker | Calendar-based date range selection for dashboards |
| **Maps** | Leaflet.js / react-leaflet | Interactive geo-distribution maps |
| **Drag & Drop** | @dnd-kit | Funnel builder and dashboard layout customization |
| **Real-time** | Socket.io client | Live event stream on real-time dashboard |

### 6.2 Backend / API

| Category | Technology | Purpose |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| **Runtime** | Node.js 22 LTS | JavaScript server runtime |
| **API Framework** | Next.js API Routes + Fastify | Next.js for app APIs; Fastify for high-throughput ingestion endpoint |
| **Language** | TypeScript | Shared types with frontend |
| **Authentication** | NextAuth.js v5 (Auth.js) | OAuth (Google/GitHub), magic links, JWT sessions |
| **Authorization** | CASL | Attribute-based access control (ABAC) for multi-tenant RBAC |
| **Schema Validation** | Zod | Runtime payload validation on ingestion API |
| **ORM (Postgres)** | Drizzle ORM | Type-safe SQL for relational data (users, workspaces, billing) |
| **API Documentation** | OpenAPI + @hono/swagger-ui | Auto-generated API docs |
| **Email** | Resend / Nodemailer | Transactional email delivery |
| **Payments** | Stripe | Subscription billing, metered billing |
| **Rate Limiting** | Upstash Redis (rate-limit library) | Per-tenant API ingestion rate limiting |
| **Job Queue** | BullMQ (Redis-backed) | Async jobs: report generation, scheduled emails |
| **WebSockets** | Socket.io server | Real-time event push to dashboard |
| **Caching** | Redis (ioredis) | API key validation cache, session cache, query cache |
| **File Storage** | MinIO (S3-compatible) | Report PDF storage, SDK binary hosting |

### 6.3 Data Pipeline (Event Ingestion & Processing)

| Category | Technology | Purpose |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| **Message Broker** | Apache Kafka (KRaft mode) | Durable, high-throughput event stream buffer |
| **Kafka Client** | KafkaJS | Node.js Kafka producer for ingestion API |
| **OLAP Database** | ClickHouse | Columnar analytical database for all event data |
| **ClickHouse Driver** | @clickhouse/client | Official Node.js client |
| **Stream Processing** | ClickHouse Kafka Engine | Native Kafka → ClickHouse consumer (no extra middleware) |
| **Materialized Views** | ClickHouse MVs | Pre-aggregated rollups for common dashboard queries |
| **GeoIP** | MaxMind GeoLite2 | IP address → Country/City resolution (on ingestion server) |
| **PII Sanitization** | Custom middleware | SHA-256 hashing of emails/IPs, keyword blocklist stripping |
| **Schema** | MergeTree (tenant_id, event_name, timestamp) | Optimal sort key for multi-tenant analytical queries |

### 6.4 Relational Database (OLTP)

| Category | Technology | Purpose |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| **Database** | PostgreSQL 16 | Users, workspaces, billing, tracking rules, SDK configurations |
| **Migrations** | Drizzle Kit | Version-controlled schema migrations |
| **Connection Pooling** | PgBouncer | Connection pooling for serverless environments |

### 6.5 Infrastructure & DevOps

| Category | Technology | Purpose |
|----------|-----------|---------|
| **Containerization** | Docker + Docker Compose | Local dev environment orchestration |
| **Container Orchestration** | Kubernetes (K8s) | Production deployment and auto-scaling |
| **IaC** | Terraform | Infrastructure provisioning (cloud-agnostic) |
| **Reverse Proxy** | Nginx | Load balancing, SSL termination, static serving |
| **SSL** | Let's Encrypt + Certbot | Free TLS certificates |
| **Monitoring** | Prometheus + Grafana | Infrastructure and application metrics |
| **Logging** | OpenTelemetry + Loki + Grafana | Distributed tracing and log aggregation |
| **Error Tracking** | Sentry (self-hosted) | Application error monitoring |
| **CI/CD** | GitHub Actions | Automated testing, linting, Docker image builds, deployments |
| **Registry** | GitHub Container Registry (GHCR) | Docker image storage |

### 6.6 SDKs & Plugins Tech Stack

| Platform | Language | Key Libraries |
|----------|----------|--------------|
| **JavaScript (Web)** | TypeScript | Vanilla TS, MutationObserver, History API, PostMessage |
| **WordPress/WooCommerce** | PHP 8.1+ | WordPress Plugin API, WooCommerce hooks, wp_remote_post |
| **Magento 2** | PHP 8.1+ | Magento Observer, Layout XML, MessageQueue, REST Client |
| **PrestaShop** | PHP 8.1+ | PrestaShop MVC, Hook system, Curl |
| **Shopify** | Node.js + PHP | Shopify API, Webhook handlers, App Bridge |
| **Unity** | C# / .NET | UnityWebRequest, SQLite, JsonUtility, PlayerPrefs |
| **Android** | Kotlin | OkHttp, Room DB, Gson, Lifecycle Components |
| **React Native** | TypeScript | AsyncStorage, React Navigation, Expo APIs |
| **iOS** | Swift 5.9+ | URLSession, SQLite.swift, SwiftUI, Combine |

