## Implementation Priority (MVP → Full Platform)

### Phase 1 — MVP (Months 1-4)
- [ ] SaaS Storefront (marketing + auth)
- [ ] Core User Dashboard (pageviews, sessions, traffic sources)
- [ ] JavaScript Web SDK (autocapture)
- [ ] WordPress + WooCommerce Plugin
- [ ] Kafka + ClickHouse data pipeline
- [ ] Stripe billing integration
- [ ] Team invitations & multi-project support

### Phase 2 — Growth (Months 5-8)
- [ ] Visual Event Tagger (iframe + postMessage)
- [ ] Funnel Analysis + Cohort Retention
- [ ] Android + iOS Native SDKs
- [ ] React Native SDK
- [ ] Magento 2 + PrestaShop modules
- [ ] Shopify App Store submission
- [ ] Admin Super Dashboard

### Phase 3 — Scale (Months 9-12)
- [ ] Unity C# SDK + Game Analytics Dashboard
- [ ] Real-Time Dashboard (Socket.io)
- [ ] Anomaly Detection & Alerts
- [ ] Scheduled Reports & PDF exports
- [ ] A/B Testing module (feature flags)
- [ ] Predictive AI analytics (ML pipeline)
- [ ] Self-hosted / on-premise deployment option
